    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. While it shows a few light signs of its adventures, the interior is clean and the performance is solid, making it a wonderful choice for anyone seeking a dependable and stylish ride!",
